#CircuitBreakerSG D-40

When it's the weekend, let's have some weekend vibes. How about some cinnamon french toast dunk in maple syrup? Sipping cold sparkling @HelmigsCurcumin Noni effervescent drink and Netflix-ing away.

Noni extract is said to increase body's immune system, antioxidant, reduce inflammation, etc. Empirically it is also believed to be able to improve digestive system and relieve joint pain. Have you tried this before?

Happy weekend 🌻
